      <title>裕信银行收购德国商业银行引发德国国内争议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/unicredits-commerzbank-swoop-fires-up-divisive-debate-germany-2024-09-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[裕信银行（UniCredit）对德国商业银行（Commerzbank）的收购开局再次引发了有关德国银行业未来的争论，促使柏林方面暂停出售该银行的股份，并将焦点转向德意志银行（Deutsche Bank）作为潜在的竞争对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/unicredits-commerzbank-swoop-fires-up-divisive-debate-germany-2024-09-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 17:16:43 GMT</pubDate>
